Canonical names of the 15 European tender-panel countries in scope:

{=% for canonical, aliases in countries.items() =%}
- **{= canonical =}**{= " (also written as: " + (aliases | join(", ")) + ")" if aliases else "" =}
{=% endfor =%}

Map the submitted country name to its canonical form above. Accept English / native-language / native-script / common-abbreviation variants pointing to the same country, plus minor punctuation, diacritic, spacing, and capitalization variants.

Any jurisdiction outside the 15-country panel — Norway, Switzerland, other EFTA states, microstates, candidate states, supranational regions such as the European Union, broader subregions such as Scandinavia or the Balkans, or non-European jurisdictions — maps to `{{ CANONICAL_INVALID }}`.
